data.description: PRICE REDUCED AND NEW ROOF INSTALLED !!!  Welcome to your dream home in the picturesque community of Vista Grande, Clermont! This meticulously maintained single-story residence is a true gem, offering both a comfortable living space and the perfect blend of modern elegance.  The OPEN FLOORPLAN seamlessly connects the kitchen, living, and dining areas, creating an inviting space for family gatherings and entertaining. This home truly shows like a model home with its stylish finishes and attention to detail. This cleverly designed layout places the master suite on one side and the three additional bedrooms on the other, ensuring ultimate privacy and tranquility for all family members and guests.   Step outside to a lovely FENCED BACKYARD providing a secure area for play and relaxation, while the SCREENED-IN PATIO allows you to savor the serene view and Florida's beautiful weather. The sellers have invested in your future by having a BRAND-NEW ROOF installed. The OVERSIZED garage is ideal to park your 2 cars and also having a large space for you to work on your weekend projects.   Clermont, FL, is renowned for its proximity to an array of stunning lakes and natural parks. Immerse yourself in the beauty of the outdoors right in your own backyard. Enjoy the convenience of nearby shopping and dining options just minutes away, making everyday errands a breeze.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your new home. Contact us today for more information or to schedule a private showing.
